'''VRChat Official Pride Hub''' is a world collaboration between VRChat and the community to celebrate [[Pride Month 2025|Pride Month]] for 2025. 

==Announcements==
[[File:Vrc pridemonth contentguides.jpeg|thumb|An image uploaded to VRChat's social media accounts, to inform users about an upcoming Pride Month collaboration event.]]
On April 25, 2025, VRChat posted on their social media accounts<ref>"Celebrate Pride Month in #VRChat with us!" - posted by VRChat on [https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com/post/3lno7k6jps223 Bluesky], [https://www.threads.com/@officialvrchat/post/DI4qgKZOOE5 Threads] and [https://twitter.com/VRChat/status/1915887001372684394 Twitter].</ref> regarding their plans to launch a Parade Pride Hub World.

{{Quote|''Celebrate Pride Month in #VRChat with us! 

We're looking for posters (public) and Pride Floats (invite only) for a Pride Month-themed world, similar to NYE. Please review the guidelines here:
https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1xT84ES2ouMHcSRN9TmCYc7Z5nYNnmd4wZ8DrFZKvZKE

Forms open on May 2! We can't wait to see your submissions!''}}

Submissions for posters and floats open on May 2nd, and close on May 30 at 12 P.M. (PST); all submissions are final. There are 35 available community poster slots, and must be LGBTQ+ themed. There are 10 slots available for pride floats, but are allowed to be submitted through an invite-only process.

